            <h2 class="h5 mb-2">2. Cancellations by Families</h2>

            <h3 class="h6">Single-Day or Single-Session Purchases</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Refunds available if canceled at least <strong>24 hours before</strong> the session.</li>
                <li>No refunds for cancellations within 24 hours or missed sessions.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h6">Weekly Packages</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Refunds allowed up to <strong>48 hours before</strong> the first weekly session.</li>
                <li>No refunds once the week has started.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h6">Monthly Packages</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Refunds allowed up to <strong>5 days before</strong> the month begins.</li>
                <li>No refunds after the month begins.</li>
                <li>A one-time credit may be issued for documented emergencies.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Program Cancellations by The Mignone HIVE -->
    <div class="mb-4">
