            <h2 class="h5 mb-2">3. Program Cancellations by The Mignone HIVE</h2>
            <p>If a session is canceled due to staff illness, emergencies, or other unforeseen circumstances:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Families will receive a <strong>full refund</strong> or equal-value program credit.</li>
                <li>Long-term closures of a week or more will be refunded proportionally.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Non-Attendance -->
    <div class="mb-4">
        <div>
            <h2 class="h5 mb-2">4. Non-Attendance</h2>
            <p>No refunds or credits are given for absences, including illness, unless The HIVE cancels the session.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Special Programs -->
